    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_comical-01.m4a"
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_pop-01.m4a"
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_meeting-01.m4a"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_02_01-rui001.m4a",
      "text": "おはようございます\n{user}さん",
      "startTime": 2.2333333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
      "startTime": 0.43333333333333335
    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_door-open-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_02_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "おはよう、早いね\nまだ約束の30分前だ",
      "startTime": 6.166666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_02_01-rui002.m4a",
      "text": "……ひょっとして、早過ぎましたか？\nつい、いつものクセで……すみません",
      "startTime": 11.733333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_02_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "今日は話だけだし、あまり身構えないで大丈夫だよ\nここは君の事務所なんだから、リラックスしてくれ",
      "startTime": 20.766666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_02_01-rui003.m4a",
      "text": "でもバンプロの時、事務所では\nいつも緊張感を持つようにしていました",
      "startTime": 26.633333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_02_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "バンプロでは、打ち合わせでもそんな空気なのか？",
      "startTime": 29.533333333333335,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_02_01-rui004.m4a",
      "text": "バンプロというか、父――朝倉社長の前では……\nどうしても……",
      "startTime": 38.733333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_02_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "俺の手本は三枝さんだからな……\n星見プロは三枝さんに似て、もっとおおらかな社風だよ",
      "startTime": 43.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_02_01-rui005.m4a",
      "text": "そうなんです。バンプロとまるで雰囲気が違うので\n最初の頃は私達、戸惑っていたんですよ",
      "startTime": 52.166666666666664,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_02_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "朝倉さんと三枝さんの性格の差かもしれないな\nもしかして、やりにくい？",
      "startTime": 60.166666666666664,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_02_01-rui006.m4a",
      "text": "まさか、そんなことは全然ありません\n楽しいですよ",
      "startTime": 65.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_02_01-rui007.m4a",
      "text": "優やすみれとも、よく話してるんです\n星見プロを選んでよかったって",
      "startTime": 70.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_02_01-rui008.m4a",
      "text": "私達を受け入れてくれて\n本当にありがとうございました",
      "startTime": 75.76666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_02_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "改めて言われると、くすぐったいな\n俺も全力でTRINITYAiLEをサポートするよ",
      "startTime": 82,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_02_01-rui009.m4a",
      "text": "ありがとうございます！\nこのご恩は、仕事でお返しします",
      "startTime": 87.03333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_02_01-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "天動さんは真面目だな……\nでも、そうなると……やっぱりこの仕事は……",
      "startTime": 93.53333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_02_01-rui010.m4a",
      "text": "？　どうしたんですか？　{user}さん\n急に視線が泳ぎ出しましたけど",
      "startTime": 103.33333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_02_01-rui011.m4a",
      "text": "トリエルに仕事のオファーが来ていて\n今日はその打ち合わせなんですよね？",
      "startTime": 108.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_02_01-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "トリエルじゃなくて\n天動さん単独のオファーなんだけど……",
      "startTime": 113.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_02_01-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "……やっぱり天動さん向きじゃない気がしてきた\nごめん、再検討させてもらっていいか？",
      "startTime": 119.86666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_02_01-rui012.m4a",
      "text": "待って下さい！　どんな話なのかも聞いてないのに\n断るなんて……話くらい、聞かせて下さい",
      "startTime": 126.36666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_02_01-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "いや、しかし……",
      "startTime": 130.63333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_02_01-rui013.m4a",
      "text": "私だってプロのアイドルです！\n今までだって、どんな仕事もやり遂げてきました",
      "startTime": 135,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_02_01-rui014.m4a",
      "text": "星見プロの看板を傷つけるようなことは絶対しません\n{user}さん、信じて下さい！",
      "startTime": 142.93333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_02_01-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "天動さんを信じてないんじゃないよ\nただ、人には向き不向きがあるだろ？",
      "startTime": 148.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_02_01-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "今回のオファーはファッション誌のグラビアなんだ\n歌でも踊りでもない",
      "startTime": 154.76666666666668,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_02_01-rui015.m4a",
      "text": "グラビアなら、今までだってやったことあります\nアイドルとして想定内のお仕事です",
      "startTime": 160.43333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_02_01-rui016.m4a",
      "text": "出版社さんにせっかく私を指名していただいたのに\n無下にしたくはありません",
      "startTime": 167.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_02_01-koh013.m4a",
      "text": "ちょ……ちょっと待ってくれ。積極的なのはいいけど\n内容を正確に把握しないで仕事を受けるのはよくないよ",
      "startTime": 173.06666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_02_01-rui017.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さんが信用出来る方だというのは\n今まで一緒にお仕事をしてきて、よく分かってますから",
      "startTime": 180.06666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_02_01-koh014.m4a",
      "text": "うっ、そんなにまっすぐな目で言われると\nますます、説明しづらいな……",
      "startTime": 188.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_02_01-rui018.m4a",
      "text": "ファッション誌のグラビアなんですよね？\nさっきから、どうしてモゴモゴしてるんですか？",
      "startTime": 194.96666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_02_01-koh015.m4a",
      "text": "分かった、内容を説明する\nそれを聞いたうえで、嫌なら遠慮なく言ってくれ",
      "startTime": 201.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_02_01-rui019.m4a",
      "text": "私の返事は「はい」か「イエス」のどちらかです",
      "startTime": 205.23333333333332,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_02_01-koh016.m4a",
      "text": "こらこら全肯定はダメだって……\n雑誌はB.B。巻頭で特集を組んでくれる",
      "startTime": 213.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_02_01-rui020.m4a",
      "text": "有名な女性向けファッション誌ですよね\n凄くいいお話じゃないですか",
      "startTime": 220.96666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_02_01-koh017.m4a",
      "text": "その特集の内容が、夏の水着特集なんだ\nだから、けっこう露出度が高いんだけど……",
      "startTime": 228.13333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
